"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#9. **Summary and Review Notes** - At regular intervals (weekly or monthly), review your notes and create summary notes. This will help consolidate your knowledge and reveal areas that need more attention or where your understanding has changed.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#9. **Summary and Review Notes** - At regular intervals (weekly or monthly), review your notes and create summary notes. This will help consolidate your knowledge and reveal areas that need more attention or where your understanding has changed.","outlinks":[],"size":249,"hash":"36072af40463779f68cb1280734c372f8e39fd051f79fd3adfdf2f8d4b19ae09"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#10. **Quotes and Insights Collection** - Collect quotes and insights that resonate with you. Given your background and curiosity, this could be a mix of reflections on technology, AI, and even personal thoughts. Link them to related topics or create a dedicated \"wisdom\" vault.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#10. **Quotes and Insights Collection** - Collect quotes and insights that resonate with you. Given your background and curiosity, this could be a mix of reflections on technology, AI, and even personal thoughts. Link them to related topics or create a dedicated \"wisdom\" vault.","outlinks":[],"size":282,"hash":"5cdd9f67666da8d137fe33a2255fdc45a1cdfb7acc5a0c8631e87da55549d17f"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#11. **Linking Concepts to Videos** - Since you watch a lot of AI content on YouTube, take brief notes on the key points from videos, and link these notes to broader concepts in your vault. Add a timestamp to the video for easy reference.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#11. **Linking Concepts to Videos** - Since you watch a lot of AI content on YouTube, take brief notes on the key points from videos, and link these notes to broader concepts in your vault. Add a timestamp to the video for easy reference.","outlinks":[],"size":242,"hash":"92c80622bc4bedc49ec38565e22ee890eda8f8760ffcdc2c2be941aa08078cfb"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#12. **Idea Incubation Area** - Have a section where you collect half-formed ideas or brainstorming sessions. This is a space to be messy and spontaneous—where early thoughts can evolve into more structured notes.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#12. **Idea Incubation Area** - Have a section where you collect half-formed ideas or brainstorming sessions. This is a space to be messy and spontaneous—where early thoughts can evolve into more structured notes.","outlinks":[],"size":217,"hash":"13728ec271b1687fbc2078d859f729be8bfdb45b99ec0f665a424b626b148c30"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#13. **Personal Narratives** - Record personal stories, especially those related to your experiences in IT or reflections on changes in technology. These could eventually become valuable anecdotes, especially for your grandchildren.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#13. **Personal Narratives** - Record personal stories, especially those related to your experiences in IT or reflections on changes in technology. These could eventually become valuable anecdotes, especially for your grandchildren.","outlinks":[],"size":236,"hash":"b8f15ace527895545ae5b59e4758b32b82d4f3b6267e652fb0995c3819754585"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#14. **Templates** - Use templates for common note types to ensure consistency. For example, create templates for book notes, video summaries, research topics, or daily logs.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#14. **Templates** - Use templates for common note types to ensure consistency. For example, create templates for book notes, video summaries, research topics, or daily logs.","outlinks":[],"size":178,"hash":"4dab9c8826a2c02814db57a83b563a74791a08e27e08990d3d1a34085c92544c"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#15. **Periodic \"MOC\" (Map of Content) Notes** - Create \"Map of Content\" notes to organize areas of interest like \"AI Avatars\" or \"The Mind and Brain.\" These MOCs are like tables of content that help you navigate your notes efficiently.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#15. **Periodic \"MOC\" (Map of Content) Notes** - Create \"Map of Content\" notes to organize areas of interest like \"AI Avatars\" or \"The Mind and Brain.\" These MOCs are like tables of content that help you navigate your notes efficiently.","outlinks":[],"size":240,"hash":"6d0845da77bbc19f61e10bc79f94c4a3ca174caa621c09e5277601a120c532de"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#16. **Knowledge Gaps** - Keep a section of each note dedicated to what you don’t know. This helps identify areas for further research, and it's great for feeding your ongoing curiosity.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#16. **Knowledge Gaps** - Keep a section of each note dedicated to what you don’t know. This helps identify areas for further research, and it's great for feeding your ongoing curiosity.","outlinks":[],"size":190,"hash":"b7b6474563dfc134aed83e567810b7131a0aa39d65c721a1a4a0adacbb90fa14"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#17. **Linking to Personal Reflections** - Since you’re interested in the mind and brain, regularly link abstract concepts to your personal experience. This helps integrate new knowledge with personal insights, deepening understanding.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#17. **Linking to Personal Reflections** - Since you’re interested in the mind and brain, regularly link abstract concepts to your personal experience. This helps integrate new knowledge with personal insights, deepening understanding.","outlinks":[],"size":239,"hash":"d4529b7feb6e8129a697d62ebcf056cad48e33461137dd0b58e3e22e46609e4c"}
"SmartBlock:Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#18. **Voice Notes** - If typing isn't convenient sometimes, consider recording voice notes to capture thoughts on the go. You could transcribe these into written notes later if desired.": {"class_name":"SmartBlock","embeddings":{},"key":"Note Making.md##Brainstorming Ideas#18. **Voice Notes** - If typing isn't convenient sometimes, consider recording voice notes to capture thoughts on the go. You could transcribe these into written notes later if desired.","outlinks":[],"size":189,"hash":"bc8f28dffab2603c719879d3ed9f5a039facd23611dafdd0e3e8cc273830aaee"}